title: Keep the West alive. Pass on knowledge, wisdom, good morals, and an appreciation for the West to the next generation. Pass it on to your family and your wider community.

author.bio: Don't take life too seriously.
author.bio_html: Don't take life too seriously.

body:
Kill the west I say. Instead of holding to tradition, let us look for new traditions:

I think we should start some new action groups.

One such group I would consider would be one where we pursue 'old world' pursuits, as both a novelty, and with the greater goal of adopting some or all of the priniciples outlined in the old world.

This is the part where it gets fun!!
